WEBVTT

00:02.207 --> 00:08.541
Japan's Princess Mako gave up her title and married her college sweetheart, Kei Komuro, on Tuesday.

00:08.992 --> 00:11.751
The couple forewent the usual pomp that makes a royal wedding,...

00:12.176 --> 00:16.181
...and instead had an official submit paperwork to a local office in the morning.

00:16.629 --> 00:21.504
Mako also refused to receive a one-off payment of about 1.3 million dollars,...

00:21.961 --> 00:24.553
...typically made to princesses when they marry.

00:25.009 --> 00:30.850
The understated wedding follows a four-year engagement beset by scandal, delay and mental anguish.

